    public static class ForgeGuiFactory.ForgeConfigGui.GeneralEntry
extends GuiConfigEntries.CategoryEntry
    This custom list entry provides the General Settings entry on the Minecraft Forge Configuration screen. It extends the base Category entry class and defines the IConfigElement objects that will be used to build the child screen.
